<br />&quot;Love isn't love until you give it away, so give it wings and let it go, if it's meant to be it will fly right back to you!&quot;
<br />&quot;No matter how hard things seem, true love will aide you through it.&quot;
<br />&quot;When during sad times an angel should come to you, open your eyes and see who that angel is, for that is your one true love.&quot;
